{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Glass Shader"], "type": "title", "extent": [0, 17], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [81, 125], "text": ["A physically plausible glass shader."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [179, 507], "text": ["Controls how dull a surface appears. A value of ", {"text": ["0.0"], "type": "code"}, " results in a smooth surface with perfectly sharp reflections. A value of ", {"text": ["1.0"], "type": "code"}, " produces a completely dull surface. Under the hood, this simulates microscopic bumps which become more pronounced the higher the ", {"text": ["Roughness"], "type": "ui"}, ", causing reflected light to be scattered more."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Roughness"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "rough"}, "extent": [152, 164], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [525, 579], "text": ["The index of refraction of the surface material."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["IOR"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "ior"}, "extent": [507, 512], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [613, 644], "text": ["The color of reflections."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Reflect Color"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "reflcolor"}, "extent": [579, 594], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [678, 709], "text": ["The color of refractions."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Refract Color"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "refrcolor"}, "extent": [644, 659], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["General"], "extent": [137, 152], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [757, 839], "text": ["Tints light with the ", {"text": ["Attenuation Color"], "type": "ui"}, " as it travels through the object."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Enable"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "attenenable"}, "extent": [727, 736], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [866, 925], "text": ["The material\u2019s interior color to be used for tinting."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Color"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "attencolor"}, "extent": [839, 846], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [968, 1052], "text": ["The density of the interior, higher values tint more over a shorter distances."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Attenuation Density"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "attendensity"}, "extent": [925, 946], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Attenuation"], "extent": [709, 727], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1108, 1177], "text": ["Fake caustic refractions by making the object semi-transparent."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Enable"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "fakecausticenable"}, "extent": [1072, 1081], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [174, 285], "text": ["Controls how much the light passing through is tinted by the ", {"text": ["Refract Color"], "type": "ui"}, " and ", {"text": ["Attenuation Color"], "type": "ui"}, "."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Transmission Tint"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "fakecaustictransmit"}, "extent": [1177, 1196], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "extent": [309, 460], "text": ["At ", {"text": ["1"], "type": "code"}, ", only the fraction of light transmitted through the surface (See ", {"text": ["kt"], "type": "ui"}, " input) is used for caustics, At ", {"text": ["0"], "type": "code"}, ", all light is allowed to pass."]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "extent": [460, 708], "text": ["A value of ", {"text": ["1"], "type": "code"}, ", which is more physically plausible, creates darker edges around object shadows. This occurs because when light hits an object at a grazing angle, less of the light is transmitted through the object and more of it is reflected."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Shadow"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"id": "fakecausticshadow"}, "extent": [1277, 1285], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Fake Caustics"], "extent": [1052, 1072], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Parameters", "role": "section", "extent": [125, 137], "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "id": "parameters"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1371, 1404], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/brushedmetalshader", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/brushedmetalshader"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1404, 1432], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/carpaintshader", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/carpaintshader"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1432, 1451], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/glass", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/glass"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1451, 1481], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/principledshader", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/principledshader"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1481, 1507], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/surfacemodel", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/surfacemodel"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1507, 1530], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/layercomp", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/layercomp"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1530, 1552], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/layermix", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/layermix"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1552, 1575], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/layerpack", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/layerpack"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1575, 1600], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/layerunpack", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/layerunpack"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1600, 1631], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/setlayercomponent", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/vop/setlayercomponent"}]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Related", "role": "section", "extent": [1362, 1371], "container": true, "type": "related_section", "id": "related"}], "title": ["Glass Shader"], "summary": ["A physically plausible glass shader."], "attrs": {"since": "14.5", "namespace": null, "version": null, "context": "vop", "type": "node", "internal": "glassshader"}, "included": ["/nodes/vop/fakecaustics"], "type": "root"}